              <p><em>“We are excited to achieve record sales for the 2nd consecutive year”, commented Todd Schnack, President &amp; CEO of DTS. “We were successful in expanding our customer base across several geographies which will continue to benefit us moving forward. We are also very pleased with our strong bottom line results for the year. We continue to be optimistic in regards to the long term revenue and profit growth opportunities for our company.”</em></p>
