              <p>Dynamic Test Solutions (DTS) a Singapore private limited company and MC Test Products, Inc., a California corporation, have announced that they will merge. The two companies are leaders in the design and fabrication of ATE and non-ATE semiconductor test hardware including final test loadboards, wafer test hardware, laboratory boards, and turn-key solutions.</p>
              <p><em>“We are very excited about the synergies of our merger with MC Test”, commented Todd Schnack, President &amp; CEO of DTS. “The products and services that we will be able to provide our combined global customer base moving forward become significantly broader. The merger will also accelerate our expansion into the key Silicon Valley market.”</em></p>
